text: #2 is an EP by Suburban Kids with Biblical Names, released on May 18, 2005 by Labrador Records. "Funeral Face" was the only track to be carried on to their album #3. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2005 EPs Category:Suburban Kids with Biblical Names EPs Category:Labrador Records EPs
